OL,3,CLabour to include Burnham in candidate
OL,4,Cselection for Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FLabour's ruling body has granted Andy
OL,7,FBurnham permission to put himself
OL,8,Fforward for the upcoming Makerfield by-
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,12,Fannounced on Thursday 14 May his
OL,13,Fintention to stand in the by-election,
OL,14,Fafter the constituency's current MP
OL,15,Fsaid he would stand down to make way
OL,16,Ffor Burnham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
