OL,3,CLabour to include Burnham in candidate
OL,4,Cselection for Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Labour party said:
OL,7,F"Labour's ruling body, the National
OL,8,FExecutive Committee has today given
OL,9,Fpermission to Andy Burnham to stand in
OL,10,Fthe candidate selection process in the
OL,11,Fforthcoming by-election for the
OL,12,FMakerfield constituency."
OL,14,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester has
OL,15,Flong been seen as a potential rival to
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer, but he has been
OL,17,Funable to officially challenge the
OL,18,FPrime Minister because he is not a
OL,19,Fsitting MP.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
