OL,3,CLabour to include Burnham in candidate
OL,4,Cselection for Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FAndy Burnham previously attempted to
OL,7,Fstand as the Labour candidate in the
OL,8,FGorton and Denton by-election, but his
OL,9,Fbid was blocked by Labour's National
OL,10,FExecutive Committee.
OL,12,FThe committee cited the cost to the
OL,13,Ftax payer and the party if a Mayoral
OL,14,Felection was to take place to replace
OL,15,FMr Burnham as the Mayor of Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
