OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779091568
OL,3,CLabour to include Burnham in candidate
OL,4,Cselection for Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FBut a number of critics accused the
OL,7,FPrime Minister of blocking Andy
OL,8,FBurnham's attempt to run out of fear
OL,9,Fhe would mount a leadership challenge
OL,10,Fif he made it to Parliament.
OL,12,FFormer Deputy Leader and Ashton-under-
OL,13,FLyne MP Angela Rayner said the
OL,14,Fdecision to block Mr Burnham from
OL,15,Frunning as an MP was a "mistake".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
