OL,3,CLabour to include Burnham in candidate
OL,4,Cselection for Makerfield by-election
OL,6,FReform UK has promised to "throw
OL,7,Fabsolutely everything" at a by-
OL,8,Felection in Makerfield, where Labour
OL,9,FMP Josh Simons has announced he will
OL,10,Fstand down to allow Greater Manchester
OL,11,FMayor Andy Burnham a path back to
OL,12,FParliament.
OL,14,FNigel Farage, the leader of Reform,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We look forward to the contest
OL,16,Fand we will throw absolutely
OL,17,Feverything at it."
